{4020}{}{Who are the salvagers?}
{5000}{}{A bit to the south of here you will find an big, radiated crater. There has been an big cathedral once- the building exploded many years ago. Since then, the place is radiated... Up a little bit to the north and to the west, you got the Followers of the apocalypse. They are all peace-types. I think I don't really like them, but hey... they teach people about knowledge and stuff, *for free* ...}
