{7000}{}{We are the police force for Adytum and most parts of the Boneyard. Or let's say, we help the salvagers with their job... Most folks 'round here know enough not to cause any trouble. We already exists since a long time. Last time we got some serious trouble was with some folks called "the Blades".}
